When fetching a file from GridFS the instance of the file contains _id, chunkSize, length and md5, but not uploadDate. The uploadDate field is mentioned here: http://www.mongodb.org/display/DOCS/GridFS+Specification

Example:

{code}
<?php
$mongo = new Mongo();
$database = $mongo->test;
$grid = $database->getGridFS();

// Store file
$id = $grid->storeBytes('Some content');

// Fetch file
$file = $grid->get($id);
var_dump($file->file);
{code}

